      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/wave-equation/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.0,
      "size": 31968,
      "text": "你有没有观察过，向平静的湖面扔一颗石子会产生什么？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "wave-equation",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/wave-equation/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.56,
      "size": 24912,
      "text": "涟漪从落点向外扩散，这就是波的传播。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "wave-equation",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-4",
      "filename": "intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/wave-equation/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.57,
      "size": 25200,
      "text": "波动方程正是描述这种现象的数学工具。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "wave-equation",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-1",
      "filename": "concept-concept-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/wave-equation/xiaoxiao/concept-concept-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.57,
      "size": 25200,
      "text": "波动方程描述了扰动如何在介质中传播。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "wave-equation",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-2",
      "filename": "concept-concept-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/wave-equation/xiaoxiao/concept-concept-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.56,
      "size": 40896,
      "text": "它的核心是：位移的时间二阶导数等于空间二阶导数乘以波速的平方。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "wave-equation",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-3",
      "filename": "concept-concept-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/wave-equation/xiaoxiao/concept-concept-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.04,
      "size": 32688,
      "text": "这个方程适用于声波、水波、电磁波等各种波动现象。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "wave-equation",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-4",
      "filename": "concept-concept-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/wave-equation/xiaoxiao/concept-concept-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.32,
      "size": 21168,
      "text": "让我们通过可视化来观察波的行为。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "wave-equation",
      "section_id": "propagation",
      "line_id": "prop-1",
      "filename": "propagation-prop-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/wave-equation/xiaoxiao/propagation-prop-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.27,
      "size": 20304,
      "text": "观察一根弦上的波是如何传播的。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "wave-equation",
      "section_id": "propagation",
      "line_id": "prop-2",
