      "path": "audio/narrations/wave-equation/xiaoxiao/propagation-prop-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.81,
      "size": 28944,
      "text": "初始的扰动分成两部分，分别向左和向右传播。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "wave-equation",
      "section_id": "propagation",
      "line_id": "prop-3",
      "filename": "propagation-prop-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/wave-equation/xiaoxiao/propagation-prop-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.88,
      "size": 30096,
      "text": "波的形状在传播过程中保持不变，只是位置在移动。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "wave-equation",
      "section_id": "propagation",
      "line_id": "prop-4",
      "filename": "propagation-prop-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/wave-equation/xiaoxiao/propagation-prop-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.59,
      "size": 25488,
      "text": "这是波动方程的一个重要特性：波形的保持。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "wave-equation",
      "section_id": "standing-wave",
      "line_id": "stand-1",
